(1, 'Written in Blood', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '0814209556', '2004-01-10', 'Ohio State University Press', 'hardcover', 230, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Written in Blood-Pieter Spierenburg</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nWRITTEN IN BLOOD<br>\r\nFATAL ATTRACTION IN ENLIGHTENMENT<br>AMSTERDAM\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nDit boek bevat twee sensationele verhalen, elk van een fatale liefde die <br>eindigt in moord. De Amsterdammers van toen, in 1766 en 1775, smulden ervan <br>en voor ons zijn ze nog steeds even spannend. <br>Een is een liefdesdriehoek: een man van deftige komaf en zijn minnares vermoorden<br> in het door hen gehuurde huis zijn echtgenote. Dan zitten de daders met het <br>probleem hoe het lijk te dumpen zonder dat er auto''s bestaan; <br>en ze worden verrast! De hoofdpersoon uit het tweede verhaal is mislukt<br> als acteur, chirurg en minnaar. Dan wordt hĳ verliefd op een <br>prostituée, die zonder dat ze dit meent belooft met hem te trouwen. <br>Een brief geschreven met zijn eigen bloed vermag haar niet over te halen.<br> Voor haar staand wil hij zelfmoord plegen maar als vanzelf draait het mes de andere kant op.\r\nVoor een tour door het oude Amsterdam langs de belangrĳkste plekken van deze liefdesdrama''s,<a href="../../../assets/maps/Amsterdam4.pdf" TARGET="_blank">fatale liefde - de tour.</a>"\r\n\r\n\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Written in Blood-Pieter Spierenburg</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nWRITTEN IN BLOOD<br>\r\nFATAL ATTRACTION IN ENLIGHTENMENT<br>AMSTERDAM\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n“In Written in Blood, Pieter Spierenburg demonstrates an almost unrivaled knowledge of eighteenth-century Amsterdam and an equally sure and deep understanding of crime and punishment within that polity.<br>This is, moreover, a stunning work of historical detection. Spierenburg has followed up every possible lead, unraveled torturous complexities, laid bare hidden<br> linkages, and—in doing so—offers a true gold mine of information about Amsterdam in the eighteenth century.” —Mary Lindemann, Carnegie Mellon University<br>\r\n\r\nThis book tells two sensational stories of fatal attraction ending in murder. Taking place in 1766 and 1775, these are as fascinating to us as they were to Amsterdamers at the time. One is a love triangle: a man from a respectable family and his lover kill his wife in their house. They face the problem of how to dump a body when there are no cars; and they are surprised! The protagonist in the second story has failed as an actor, surgeon and suitor. He falls in love with a prostitute, who insincerely promises to marry him. A letter written in blood is of no avail. He intends to commit suicide in front of her, but the knife turns the other way.\r\nFor a tour of old Amsterdam along the main sites of these love crimes,<a href="../../../assets/maps/Amsterdam4.pdf" TARGET="_blank">fatale liefde - de tour.</a>"\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10001', 'https://ohiostatepress.org/index.htm?/books/book%20pages/spierenburg%20written.html', 'y'),
(2, 'Violence and Punishment', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '0745653480', '2012-11-10', 'Polity Press', 'hardcover', 248, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title></title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nVIOLENCE AND PUNISHMENT<br>\r\nCIVILIZING THE BODY THROUGH TIME<br>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nDit boek behelst een actualisering van mijn ideeën omtrent de<br> lange-termijn ontwikkelingen in het geweld en de bestraffing tot in het heden.<br> Het breidt de discussie uit van Europa naar de Verenigde Staten en Azië<br> en behandelt daarnaast verwante thema''s als feesten en de dood.<br>Het verwerkt Norbert Elias'' theorieën over civilisatieprocessen en macht,<br> terwijl het tevens een nieuwe kijk bevat op het werk van Michel Foucault.\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>VIOLENCE AND PUNISHMENT</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nVIOLENCE AND PUNISHMENT<br>\r\nCIVILIZING THE BODY THROUGH TIME<br>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nThis book is an update of my thoughts about the long-term trends in violence and punishment up to the present. It extends the discussion from Europe to the United States and Asia, next to dealing with related subjects like festivities and death. It draws on Norbert Elias'' theories of civilizing processes and power, while also providing a reassessment of my views about Michel Foucault.</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10002', 'https://www.polity.co.uk/book.asp?ref=9780745653488', 'y'),
(3, 'The Prison Experience', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '9053569898', '2007-01-10', 'Amsterdam University Press', 'paperback', 339, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title></title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nThe Prison Experience<br>\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nDe gevangenis heeft een centrale positie in het strafrecht van de meeste landen.<br> Volgens vele historici werd gevangenschap pas in de negentiende eeuw als<br> zware juridische straf ingezet. Pieter Spierenburg corrigeert deze visie.<br> De gevangenis was in eerste instantie een disciplinair instituut en later ook<br> een strafmogelijkheid, maar altijd had de gevangenis een belangrijke rol<br> in Europese gemeenschappen van de late zestiende eeuw tot heden.\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '', 'nl', '10003', 'http://nl.aup.nl/books/9789053569894-the-prison-experience.html', 'y'),
(4, 'Social Control in Europe part1 1500 - 1800', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '0814209688', '2004-08-10', 'Ohio State Univ Press', 'hardcover', 381, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title></title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Herman Roodenburg en Spierenburg(als redacteur)<br>\r\nSOCIAL CONTROL IN EUROPE<br>\r\nVOLUME I, 1500-1800\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nEvenals het tweede deel over de moderne tijd richt dit werk zich op<br> sociale controle in de breedste zin van het woord: van bestraffing door <br>rechtbanken tot informele controle op buurtniveau. <br>Daartussenin bevond zich het instituut van de kerkelijke tucht. <br>Mijn inleiding bevat een historische en formele analyse van het concept sociale controle.\r\n\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>\r\n', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Social Control in Europe part1 1500 - 1800</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Herman Roodenburg en Pieter Spierenburg(as an editor)<br>\r\nSOCIAL CONTROL IN EUROPE<br>\r\nVOLUME I, 1500-1800\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nThis two-volume collection of essays provides a comprehensive examination of the idea of social control in the history of Europe.<br> The uniqueness of these volumes lies in two main areas. First, the contributors compare methods of social control on many levels, from police to shaming, church to guilds.<br> Second, they look at these formal and informal institutions as two-way processes.\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10004', 'https://ohiostatepress.org/index.htm?books/book%20pages/spierenburg%20social.html', 'y'),
(5, 'Social Control in Europe part2 1800 - 2000', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '0814209696', '2004-08-10', 'Ohio State University Press', 'hardcover', 445, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title></title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Clive Emsley, Eric Johnson en Spierenburg(als redacteur)<br>\r\nSOCIAL CONTROL IN EUROPE<br>\r\nVOLUME I, 1800-2000\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nEvenals het eerste deel over de vroegmoderne tijd richt dit werk zich op <br>sociale controle in de breedste zin van het woord. Speciale aandacht gaat uit <br>naar de discipline op de werkvloer in de negentiende eeuw en naar de diverse <br>dictaturen van de twintigste. <br>De auteurs tonen aan dat zelfs de "totalitaire" sociale controle verre van totaal was. <br>Mijn inleiding bevat een historische en formele analyse van het concept sociale controle.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title></title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Clive Emsley, Eric Johnson en Spierenburg(as an editor)<br>\r\nSOCIAL CONTROL IN EUROPE<br>\r\nVOLUME I, 1800-2000\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nThis two-volume collection of essays provides a comprehensive examination of the idea of social control in the history of Europe.<br> The uniqueness of these volumes lies in two main areas. First, the contributors compare methods of social control on many levels, from police to shaming, church to guilds.<br> Second, they look at these formal and informal institutions as two-way processes.\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10005', 'https://ohiostatepress.org/index.htm?books/book%20pages/spierenburg%20social.html', 'y'),
(6, 'The Spectacle of Suffering', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '0521089646', '2008-11-10', 'Cambridge University Press', 'paperback', 288, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>The Spectacle of Suffering-Pieter Spierenburg</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nTHE SPECTACLE OF SUFFERING<br>\r\nEXECUTIONS AND THE EVOLUTION OF<br> REPRESSION: FROM A PREINDUSTRIAL<br> METROPOLIS TO THE EUROPEAN EXPERIENCE \r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nMeteen na zijn eerste verschijnen in 1984 onthaalden de specialisten dit <br> als een alternatief voor Foucaults benadering van het strafsysteem. <br> zijn de geleidelijke privatisering van de bestraffing en het afnemend belang <br>van fysiek lijden daarin. <br>Die ontwikkelingen vormen weer uitingen van civilisatieprocessen, in het bijzonder <br>de tendens om de onaangename zaken des levens achter coulissen te verbergen. <br> boek was een tijd lang onverkrijgbaar, maar in 2008 kwam Cambridge UP met een heruitgave in paperback\r\n\r\n\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>The Spectacle of Suffering-Pieter Spierenburg</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nTHE SPECTACLE OF SUFFERING<br>\r\nEXECUTIONS AND THE EVOLUTION OF<br> REPRESSION: FROM A PREINDUSTRIAL<br> METROPOLIS TO THE EUROPEAN EXPERIENCE \r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nFollowing its original appearance in 1984, specialists immediately hailed this book as an alternative to Foucault''s ideas about the penal system. Key features are the gradual privatization of punishment and its decreasing association with hurting the body. These developments are expressions of civilizing processes, in particular the tendency to hide disagreeable aspects of life backstage. This book was out of print for some time, but in 2008 Cambridge UP published a paperback reprint.\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10006', 'http://www.cambridge.org/nl/academic/subjects/history/european-history-after-1450/spectacle-suffering-executions-and-evolution-repression-preindustrial-metropolis-european-experience?format=PB', 'y'),
(7, 'Men and Violence', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '0814207529', '1998-04-10', 'Ohio State University Press', 'hardcover', 304, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Men And Violence-Pieter Spierenburg</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg(als redacteur)<br>\r\nMEN AND VIOLENCE<br>\r\nGENDER, HONOR AND RITUALS IN MODERN<br> EUROPE AND AMERICA\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nUitgekomen in 1998, was dit de eerste studie die expliciet de thema''s geweld <br>en gender aan elkaar verbond. Tot dan was het concept "gender" alleen <br>op vrouwen toegepast en nog niet op het onderwerp "mannelĳkheid."<br> Veel draait om het duelleren in deze bundel. Naast het elitaire of<br> formele duel is er aandacht voor het volkse duel - alweer een <br>concept voor het eerst geformuleerd in dit boek.<br> Een van mĳn twee bĳdragen gaat over mesvechten in Amsterdam.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>\r\n', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Men And Violence-Pieter Spierenburg</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg(as an editor)<br>\r\nMEN AND VIOLENCE<br>\r\nGENDER, HONOR AND RITUALS IN MODERN<br> EUROPE AND AMERICA\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nThere is growing interest in the history of masculinity and  male culture, including violence, as an integral part of a proper understanding \r\nof gender.<br>In almost every historical setting, masculinity and violence are closely linked; certainly violent crime has been overwhelmingly a male \r\nenterprise.<br>But violence is not always criminal: in many cultural contexts violence is linked instead to honour and encoded in rituals.\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10007', 'https://ohiostatepress.org/index.htm?/books/book%20pages/spierenburg%20men.htm', 'y'),
(8, 'History of Murder', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '0745643787', '2008-07-10', 'Polity Press', 'hardcover', 300, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>History of Murder-Pieter_Spierenburg</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nA HISTORY OF MURDER<br>\r\nPERSONAL VIOLENCE IN EUROPE FROM THE MIDDLE AGES TO THE PRESENT</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>De ultieme synthese van zeven eeuwen interpersoonlijk geweld in Europa.<br> Van een breed aanvaard middel tot wraak en genoegdoening veranderde<br> moord in een tragische gebeurtenis die alom bezorgdheid wekt.<br> Tegelijkertijd daalde het moordcijfer drastisch, niettegenstaande een<br> lichte opwaartse trend sinds 1970. Belangrijk voor deze ontwikkelingen<br> waren de vergeestelijking van het mannelijk eergevoel en veranderingen in de <br>emotiehuishouding van mensen.<br> Dit boek is mede verkrijgbaar in Turkse en Koreaanse vertaling.\r\n\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>History of Murder-Pieter_Spierenburg</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nA HISTORY OF MURDER<br>\r\nPERSONAL VIOLENCE IN EUROPE FROM THE MIDDLE AGES TO THE PRESENT</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nThe ultimate synthesis of seven centuries of homicide and serious violence in Europe. Murder transformed from an often accepted means of revenge to a tragic event producing widespread anxiety. All the while the incidence of murder declined dramatically, despite a slight rise since 1970. Transformations in male honor as well as the handling of emotions are a key to these developments. This book is also available in Turkish and Korean.</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10008', 'https://www.polity.co.uk/book.asp?ref=9780745658636', 'y'),
(9, 'Please, please me''s number one', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '9089748296', '2013-10-10', 'Boom Juridische uitgevers', 'paperback', 150, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Please, please me''s number one-Pieter Spierenburg</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nPlease, please me''s number one<br>\r\nHoe was het om jong te zn in de eindeloze jaren zestig? Wat is er sindsdien veranderd? \r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nHoe was het om jong te zn in de eindeloze jaren zestig? Wat is er sindsdien veranderd? Pieter Spierenburg grijpt het  jubileum van de eerste grote<br> Beatles-hit aan voor een beschouwing over Nederland van 1963 tot nu.<br> Hij gaat vervolgens het effect na van de diverse maatschappelijke ontwikkelingen op het beeld van misdadigers en slachtoffers.<br> Daarbij ontwaart hij vier onderling verbonden trends.\r\n</h4></div></p>\r\n<!--<h3>Hard copy<a href="hardcopy.php" TARGET="_blank"> gratis </a>op te vragen</h3>-->\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Hard copy<a href="hardcopy.php" > gratis </a>op te vragen</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '', 'nl', '10009', 'http://www.bju.nl/juridisch/catalogus/please-please-mes-number-one-1', 'y'),
(10, 'The Broken Spell', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '0745653480', '1988-11-10', 'Palgrave Macmillan', 'hardcover', 313, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>The Broken Spell-Pieter Spierenburg</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2>Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nThe Broken Spell <br>\r\nA CULTURAL AND ANTHROPOLOGICAL HISTORY OF PREINDUSTRIAL EUROPE\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nDit boek geeft een synthese van de ontwikkelingen in de "lagere" cultuur in Europa van de late middeleeuwen tot ongeveer 1800.<br> Het behandelt onderwerpen zoals familie en gezin, volkscultuur, hekser?, waanzin en de doodsbeleving. <br>Het betreft een Engelse vertaling, gepubliceerd in 1991 door Rutgers UP in de Verenigde Staten en Macmillan in Engeland,<br> van de eerste Nederlandse editie uit 1988.<br> Geïnteresseerden die het Nederlands machtig zijn dienen de herziene uitgave uit 1998 ter hand te nemen.</h4></div></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>.\r\n', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>The Broken Spell-Pieter Spierenburg</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2>Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nThe Broken Spell <br>\r\nA CULTURAL AND ANTHROPOLOGICAL HISTORY OF PREINDUSTRIAL EUROPE\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nThis book provides a synthesis of developments in "low" culture in Europe from the late middle ages to about 1800. It deals with subjects such as the family, popular culture, witchcraft, madness and attitudes toward death. Published in 1991 by Rutgers UP in the United States and Macmillan in England, it is a translation of the first Dutch edition of 1988. Those interested who can read Dutch should consult the revised edition of 1998.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>\r\n\r\n', 'both', '10010', 'http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3325806-the-broken-spell', 'n'),
(11, 'Private domain, public inquiry', 'Anton Schuurman en Pieter Spierenburg ', '9065504273', '1996-07-10', 'Verloren', 'hardcover', 270, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>PRIVATE DOMAIN, PUBLIC INQUIRY</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Anton Schuurman en Pieter Spierenburg(als redacteur)<br>\r\nPRIVATE DOMAIN, PUBLIC INQUIRY<br>\r\nFAMILIES AND LIFE-STYLES IN THE NETHERLANDS AND EUROPE, 1550 TO THE PRESENT\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nDeze bundel, voortgekomen uit een conferentie in Rotterdam twee jaar ervoor, brengt een aantal Nederlandse historici samen<br> met enkele buitenlandse experts.<br> Het boek combineert twee thema''s: de geschiedenis van de verhoudingen binnen familie en gezin en die van de materiële cultuur.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>\r\n', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>PRIVATE DOMAIN, PUBLIC INQUIRY</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Anton Schuurman en Pieter Spierenburg(as an editor)<br>\r\nPRIVATE DOMAIN, PUBLIC INQUIRY<br>\r\nFAMILIES AND LIFE-STYLES IN THE NETHERLANDS AND EUROPE, 1550 TO THE PRESENT\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nThis volume brings together twelve studies centring on family and household. It''s themes include values and morals regarding family life, the family''s ties to the local community,<br>the role of objects in the house and the social character of taste. The focus is on the Netherlands but countries such as Germany, France and England are drawn into the analysis.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10011', 'http://www.verloren.nl/boeken/2086/255/817/recht/private-domain-public-inquiry', 'y'),
(12, 'Scherp toezicht', 'Cyrille Fijnaut, Pieter Spierenburg', '9060007247', '1990-07-12', 'Antiquariaat Mooi Exemplaar', 'paperback', 300, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Scherp toezicht</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Cyrille Fijnaut en Pieter Spierenburg (als redacteur)<br>\r\nScherp toezicht<br>\r\nVAN `BOEVENTUCHT'' TOT `SAMENLEVING EN CRIMINALITEIT'' <br>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nDit boek komt voort uit een conferentie ter gelegenheid van de vierhonderdste sterfdag van<br> Dirk Volkertsz Coornhert in 1990. Het verenigt historische en eigentijdse perspectieven op het<br> strafrecht. Mijn eigen bijdrage plaatst Coornherts Boeventucht (1587) in zijn historische<br> context. Het boek is uitgegeven door het thans verdwenen huis Gouda Quint maar kan<br> beschikbaar zijn in een bibliotheek bij u in de buurt.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '', 'nl', '10012', 'http://www.bol.com/nl/p/scherp-toezicht/1001004001543506/', 'y'),
(13, 'Judicial Violence in the Dutch Republic', 'Pieter Spierenburg', 'geen', '1978-07-10', 'Huisdrukkerij Universiteit van Amsterdam', 'hardcover', 247, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>JUDICIAL VIOLENCE IN THE DUTCH REPUBLIC</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2>Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nJUDICIAL VIOLENCE IN THE DUTCH REPUBLIC<br>\r\nCORPORAL PUNISHMENT, EXECUTIONS AND TORTURE IN AMSTERDAM, 1650 1750 \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nPieter Spierenburg\r\nJUDICIAL VIOLENCE IN THE DUTCH REPUBLIC\r\nCORPORAL PUNISHMENT, EXECUTIONS AND TORTURE IN AMSTERDAM, 1650 1750 [07]\r\n\r\nDit is mijn proefschrift, verdedigd aan de Universiteit van Amsterdam in 1978.<br> Het vormde de basis voor mijn Spectacle of Suffering, maar die twee boeken overlappen slechts gedeeltelijk.<br> De dissertatie heeft veel meer materiaal over Amsterdam en de Nederlandse samenleving in de vroegmoderne tijd.<br> Er is geen handelsuitgave, maar zoals gebruikelijk zijn er zo''n 100 exemplaren verspreid binnen een netwerk van landelijke en internationale bibliotheken.<br> Het kan aanwezig zijn in een bibliotheek bĳ u in de buurt.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>JUDICIAL VIOLENCE IN THE DUTCH REPUBLIC</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2>Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nJUDICIAL VIOLENCE IN THE DUTCH REPUBLIC<br>\r\nCORPORAL PUNISHMENT, EXECUTIONS AND TORTURE IN AMSTERDAM, 1650 1750 \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nThis is my dissertation, defended at the University of Amsterdam in 1978.<br> It formed the basis for my Spectacle of Suffering, but the two books overlap only partially.<br> The dissertation contains much more on Amsterdam and Dutch society in the early modern period.<br> There is no commercial edition, but according to custom about 100 copies have been distributed throughout a network of national and international libraries.<br> There may be one in a library near you.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10013', 'https://books.google.nl/books/about/Judicial_Violence_in_the_Dutch_Republic.html?id=dvdvtgAACAAJ&redir_esc=y', 'n'),
(14, 'De Verbroken Betovering', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '90-6550-042-1', '1998-03-10', 'Verloren B.V.', 'hardcover', 417, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>DE VERBROKEN BETOVERING</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nDE VERBROKEN BETOVERING<br>\r\nMENTALITEIT EN CULTUUR IN PREÏNDUSTRIEEL EUROPA \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nNa de detailstudies als Montaillou, Martin Guerre, De Koopman van Prato, enz., die alle in een zeer begrensde tijdsperiode spelen, wil deze studie een samenvatting<br> geven van het denken en voelen van de mens in het Europa van voor de Industriele Revolutie. Thema''s als volkscultuur, liefde en sex, dood en<br> begrafenis, godsdienst, lijden en geweld, en tenslotte de privatisering van het leven, worden met elkaar in verband gebracht.<br> De verzakelijking, de onttovering van de cultuur is de rode draad in het werk. Een diepzinnig boek dat toch goed leest en inzicht verschaft in de wortels van onze cultuur.<br> Een must voor (socio-)hitorici, journalisten, politici, studenten en geinteresseerde leken.<br> Het boek maakt ons hedendaagse individualisme begrijpelijk. Notenapparaat, literatuurverwijzing en register zijn uitstekend.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>DE VERBROKEN BETOVERING</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nDE VERBROKEN BETOVERING<br>\r\nMENTALITEIT EN CULTUUR IN PREÏNDUSTRIEEL EUROPA \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nPublished in 1998, this is a thoroughly revised and updated version of The Broken Spell. It provides a synthesis of developments in "low" culture in<br> Europe from the late middle ages to about 1800. After an introduction, part one covers the rise of patriarchy and its discontents; popular<br> culture and life in villages and neighborhoods; the persecution of witches.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10014', 'http://www.verloren.nl/boeken/2086/248/99/cultuur-en-mentaliteit/de-verbroken-betovering', 'y'),
(15, 'Zwarte schapen', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '9065504192', '2005-05-10', 'Verloren', 'hardcover', 153, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Zwarte schapen</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nZwarte schapen<br>\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nIn de 18e eeuw was het in Europa mogelijk familieleden die zich misdroegen bijvoorbeeld door drankzucht, geldverkwisten of losbandigheid te laten<br> opsluiten, met toestemming van de overheid en op kosten (meestal) van de familie. Spierenburg, specialist op het gebied van gevangenissen, schreef een boek<br> over de ''beterhuizen'' (particuliere gevangenissen), de bewoners, meestal de zwarte schapen van elite-families en hun geschiedenissen in de provincie Holland, van ca. 1660-1810.\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '', 'nl', '10015', 'http://www.verloren.nl/boeken/2086/257/831/sociaal-economisch/zwarte-schapen', 'y'),
(16, 'Murder and Violence in Modern Latin America', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '978-1-118-65735-5', '2013-12-10', 'Wiley-Blackwell', 'paperback', 328, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>MURDER AND VIOLENCE IN MODERN LATIN AMERICA</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Eric A. Johnson, Ricardo D. Salvatore en Pieter Spierenburg(als redacteur) <br>\r\nMURDER AND VIOLENCE IN MODERN LATIN AMERICA <br>\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nDit is het eerste resultaat in boekvorm van een ambitieus project waarin alle vormen van geweld worden geanalyseerd wereldwijd van het verre verleden tot in de moderne tijd.<br> De bijdragen aan deze studie strekken zich uit van Mexico tot Argentinië en van bendes tot genocide.<br> Het slotartikel door Ricardo Salvatore past de theorieën van Norbert Elias toe op de geschiedenis van Latijns Amerika.\r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Murder and Violence in Modern Latin America</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nEric A. Johnson, Ricardo D. Salvatore en Pieter Spierenburg(as an editor)<br>\r\nMurder and Violence in Modern Latin America<br>\r\nWritten by leading scholars from the Americas and Europe, this is a thorough assessment of state-supported murder and violence in Latin America.\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\nExamines the trajectory of murder and violence in the region over the past two centuries and elucidates theories and trends regarding violence since the end of colonial rule.<br> \r\nCovers topics such as “the disappeared,” the rise of drug cartels and narco-violence, physical violence against wives, the judging and sentencing of violent crimes, genocide, and state terrorism. \r\nExplains and applies macro-level theories regarding the rise of civilization, state building, and violence to contemporary Latin America. \r\n\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10016', 'http://eu.wiley.com/WileyCDA/WileyTitle/productCd-1118657357.html', 'y'),
(17, 'Violence in Europe: Historical and Contemporary Perspectives', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '0387745076', '2007-12-18', 'Springer', 'hardcover', 256, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>VIOLENCE IN EUROPE</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>Sophie Body-Gendrot en Pieter Spierenburg(als redacteur)<br>\r\nViolence in Europe: Historical and Contemporary Perspectives<br> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\r\n\r\nDeze bundel komt voort uit een project dat sociale wetenschappers en historici die zich met geweld bezig houden samenbracht.<br> De bijdragen strekken zich uit van huwelijksconflicten tot sport, van trends in levensdelicten tot het nachtelijk uitgaansleven.<br> Mijn eigen bijdrage gaat over de betekenis van het woord "geweld."\r\n\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Violence in Europe: Historical and Contemporary Perspectives</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>Sophie Body-Gendrot en Pieter Spierenburg (as an editor)<br>\r\nViolence in Europe: Historical and Contemporary Perspectives<br>\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nTaking the sociocultural long view, Violence in Europe analyzes the prevalence and role of violence―from street crime to terrorist attacks,<br> homicide to genocide―in the evolution of human and national behavior. The editors and 14 colleagues in history, anthropology, sociology,<br> and psychology focus on Northern and Western Europe, examining centuries of violent phenomena, from the cultural logic of the Middle Ages to today’s soccer riots<br> and security alerts.\r\n</h4>\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'both', '10017', 'http://www.springer.com/us/book/9780387745077', 'y'),
(18, 'Histoire de l''homicide en Europe', 'Pieter Spierenburg', '9782707157140', '2009-02-10', 'Presse', 'hardcover', 336, '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Histoire de l''homicide en Europe</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Laurent Mucchielli en Pieter Spierenburg(als redacteur) <br>\r\nHISTOIRE DE L''HOMICIDE EN EUROPE<br>\r\nDE LA FIN DU MOYEN ÂGE A NOS JOURS \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nDit boek introduceert de lange-termijn geschiedenis van het dodelijk geweld voor een Franstalig publiek.<br> Nagenoeg alle belangrijke experts op dit gebied leveren een bijdrage.<br> Geografisch strekt het zich uit van Scandinavië tot Spanje en Griekenland.\r\n</h4>\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '<!DOCTYPE html\r\n    PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"\r\n    "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>Histoire de l''homicide en Europe</title>\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n#cvist{\r\n\r\n	background:#F1F1F1;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n#cv {\r\n	color:brown;\r\n	\r\n    margin-top: 0.5em;\r\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    margin-left: 40px;\r\n    margin-right: auto;\r\n   \r\n    border-width: 1px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=cvist>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="omschrijving">Pieter Spierenburg<br>\r\nHistoire de l''homicide en Europe<br>\r\n\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n<h4>\r\nDans son célèbre ouvrage La Civilisation des mœurs, le sociologue allemand Norbert Elias faisait l’hypothèse de l’existence d’un processus de<br> civilisation traversant l’histoire des sociétés européennes depuis la fin du Moyen Âge et réduisant le niveau des violences physiques interpersonnelles.<br> Pourtant, l’idée d’un « retour à la violence physique » – fortement médiatisé et politisé – prédomine dans les sociétés occidentales où l’« <br> » est redevenue, au tournant du XXIe siècle, un sujet majeur.<br> \r\nReplaçant ces débats dans une perspective historique et comparative, douze historiens et sociologues, spécialistes reconnus de l’étude du crime, dressent <br> un bilan des connaissances scientifiques inédit en langue française. Ils livrent d’abord une discussion méthodologique particulièrement poussée <br>pour déterminer la valeur des statistiques en matière d’homicide et l’intérêt qu’elles représentent pour mesurer l’évolution des violences physiques dans<br> l’histoire des sociétés européennes. Ils montrent ensuite quels sont les lieux, les protagonistes (auteurs et victimes) et les motifs des homicides<br> tout au long de cette histoire, de même que le rôle qu’a joué leur répression judiciaire croissante.<br> \r\nÀ travers cette histoire du crime de sang, on voit donc aussi apparaître et s’éclairer l’histoire des rapports sociaux (entre les hommes et les femmes,<br> entre les jeunes et les vieux, entre les dominants et les dominés), l’histoire des codes sociaux et des représentations sociales (l’honneur, l’offense, la vengeance), ainsi que<br> l’histoire de la construction de l’État et de son « monopole de la violence légitime ».\r\n</h4>\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', 'fr', '10018', 'http://www.editionsladecouverte.fr/catalogue/index-Histoire_de_l_homicide_en_Europe-9782707157140.html', 'y');

