(ed.), We Have Met the Enemy and He is Us. Den Haag<br> (Studium Generale KABK) 2014: 18-31.</li><br>\r\n\r\n<li>110. Toward a Global History of Homicide and Organized Murder.<br>\r\n	     in: Crime, Histoire & Sociétés/ Crime, History & Societies 18,2 (2014): 99-116.</li><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div></ul>\r\n       <hr> <h4>N.B.: (book reviews and minor notes not included)</h4><br>\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '', 'Publication List', 'publication list,publicatie lijst', 'y', 'en'),
